Min ŋaar-ak, nu dortu gaaƴ amila min ɗo sees ka sultan aman: " Kuŋ okiŋko gay riyoy ku Buŋdi, kuŋ kuuk karmiyaaga, kuŋ kuuk aginda iŋ kuuk n̰aaɗa, oziloŋ Buŋte! "
Ansii ko, wer ka jamiyner kaak Buŋ diytu ɗo geemir goy misa iŋ ƴiriy ta sabitdi.
Ka seener, duniin taat goy ɗo duniiner-an, taar asa bire iŋ gamin okin̰co kuuk gee elgiyo. Kar ŋaar kaak gina taat Buŋ rakiyo gay, ŋaar goy doo iŋ goye ka gaasɗo.
Hiyya, min ŋa kaawiico pa-ak, ŋa gaariico pisin̰ji iŋ serpey. Min ŋaar-ak, maajirnay aawtu min ŋu taliig Rabbin Iisa.
Gem kaak gin burɗum asiiji ɗo uŋji ho ŋa loklikiiji aman: " Gem kol Rabbiney, ya ki ooy di, kiin gedire calindu ya ki ooye. "
Ɗo saan taar-an gay, nu kaawaako aman: Goyoŋ iŋ gudurre ta Ruwwin ta Buŋdi, paa kat, ku necaaɗo pey galal ta ziŋkikon di.
Ka seener, Buŋ, ŋaar rakki di kaak bera *gaanuun ɗo geemir ho kaak ɗukuma seriin ɗo geemir. Ŋaar ko kaak nec jilin̰ gee ho kaak nec ide oki. Kar kiŋ gay waa kaak kii ɗukume seriine ɗo gijiŋ?
Diŋ naa kaawe ɗo bi ka kaawin kuuk ku siirtu-aŋku: samaane ɗo gem kaak bal obe mitik.
Ɗo bi kaŋkon di, nu rawatɗo dela barkin ɗo Buŋdi ɗo bi kaŋko ho nu rawatɗo biko ɗo salaaner.
Gi iban di kadar gamin okin̰co kuuk Buŋ giniy-ak, ŋaa ginin̰co sellen̰ ɗo ŋuur kuuk elgiga, ŋuur kuuk ŋa koliig iŋ niyin ta meen̰ji.
Min gee-ak, ŋu gintu menaw ho ŋu bal okume yoo maanna. Ɗo wer-ak, Pool uctu ɗatikco ho ŋa kaawiico aman: " Gem kol siŋtay, zer ya ku cokiydu kaawor ho nu kaawko a ku ɗeetɗo min Kreet, ta-aŋ ku bal nige maanna ho taaɓin-an sa rasgikonno.
Gee ŋuur-ak, ŋuur neƴaw ho diŋ gay osgiy gee. Ŋu diya kaƴco ɗo galal ta ziŋkico di. Ŋu diya kaƴco ɗo gamin ku sokan̰ kuuk jookumo ku maaniico di. Ŋu el gaare kaawin kuuk iŋ botilcoɗo ho ŋu el gaare ziŋkico iŋ kaawin kuuk maalan di. Iŋ kaawin kuuk gelbinco raɗa, ŋu caaciya gee a ŋuu gase minninco gurus.
Ya ku talaag gee-ak, kuu ibinin̰ iŋ riy ta gamin kuuk ŋu giniyo. Gee ibanno ya ŋu amila roŋ ku *bin̰di min ɗo pompal kuuk gin pompal kuuk gin jamay. Wala ŋu amila oki pompal kuuk gin jamay kuuk gin jamay kuuk gin jamay.
Iisa gay ɗiyiiji aman: " Ŋa nun ko aŋka-aŋka kaak ki kaawiy-aŋka. "
Darre iŋ darre asa taasin̰e ho sultan iŋ sultan oki asa taasin̰e. Meya yaa un̰je ɗo werin daarin̰ ho kiɗ asa azire iŋ meya. Gamin ŋuur-aŋ okin̰co yaa gaare kadar gaase ka taaɓiner gaaye ar taar-an di.
Gi ibingig asaan Buŋ kaaw aman: " Ŋa nun meendu kat yaa kappiyin taat ŋu nigiidu. Ŋa nun meendu kat yaa kappiyin taat ŋu giniidu. " Ho pey, ŋu siir ɗo Kitamner aman: " *Rabbin Buŋ yaaco ɗukume seriin ɗo geen̰ji. "
Ŋaar-ak, min ku obit Iisa Masi ɗo gelbinko, ŋaar *Rabbine. Ampa-ak, iŋ n̰ume kaak ku n̰umtu iŋ ŋaara, jaawguwoŋ iŋ goyiŋko.
Tisik kat yaako iyin kabarrer okintiti, ŋaako iyintiŋ gamin okin̰co. Siŋte kaak gi elgiyo ho ŋa ginaat riy iŋ ginte ɗo *Rabbin Iisa Masi-ak ko.
Min Pool astu, *Yuudinna kuuk uc min Zeruzaleem asiiji moota ho ŋu diyiiji kaawin dakina kuuk raɗa ɗo gem-aka. Kar kaawin ŋuur-ak gay, ŋu bal gedire gaarin seen ta kaawco.
Kar Iisa karmiig maajirnay a ŋu kaawenno tak-tak ɗo waanna. Kar ŋu toɗiiji pey, wer gay, kaaw-at totirtu paa di.
Ŋa ceerin portikaw ɗo ŋuur kuuk goy ɗo gondikor ho ɗo kiɗ ka muuti. Ŋa yaate jaawe ɗo botol taat iya aapiye ɗo asin̰ji. "
Kar gay, ya ŋu kolin̰ciŋ ɗo teendi gay, ɓaa goy aar ta geemir. Paa kat, gem kaak kolin̰ciŋ-ak yaan̰ kaawe aman: ‟ Gem kol royay, asu! As goy uŋda. " Ansii ko, gee okin̰co kuuk asaw-ak yaan̰ bere horoomine ɗo uŋco ka siŋtan̰.
Ka seener, ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, ni ar *darjin ta Iisa Masi taat oba gala. Darjin-at yaa ɓaa ɗo ŋuur kuuk Buŋ jilaagu ho ɗo ŋuur kuuk tara ziŋkico ɗo rawtin̰co oki.
Galal ɗo ŋuur kuuk gelbinco *cawar, asaan Buŋ, ŋuu talin̰ji!
Min ŋu dortu kadar Iisa goy iŋ odinay ho ta talga, ŋu bal aamine.
Min ŋaar-ak, Iisa sin̰jiiji moota, ŋa diiriigu ho ŋa ɗiyiico aman: " Ucoŋ, dakoŋ ginenno kolaw. "
Min Iisa taliit imaanco, ŋa kaawiiji ɗo gem-ak aman: " Gem kol roŋji, zunuubinnan̰, ŋu saamiyjiŋgu. "
ho wal ŋa dawiig ɗo aki wal ɗo amiydi. Ŋa gintu pa-ak a ŋaa mate. Kar ya ki gin botol taat kii gedire gine maanna gay, tal aminduwni ho jorkinu! "
Kar gay, ginteŋ gay, gi goy ɗo portikaw. Ŋaar-ak, zeeɗinte ho gedirinte ɗo ziŋkite. Imaante iŋ ele kaak gi elgiy ziŋkite yaa goye ar garta taat goy bombo ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ho ere kaak Buŋ yaate jilinte oki, ŋaar ar goote kaak ar ɗuune ka hadinner.
Ka seener gay, mee satkiner ka tatko-ak, ŋaar ginno gudurre, ŋa gedirgiy n̰aamin̰ iŋ cigile ŋuur kuuk ibanno maanna ho kuuk rawte. Asaan meen̰ji gay, ŋaar ginno gudurre dakina.
Kar gay, kaaw taat nu siiraako-an, taar kaaw ta marbinto. Kaaw-at gaara seen ta Iisa Masi ɗo gelbinko ho ɗo gelbinko oki. Asaan gondikaw taar gaay ko bire ho portikaw taat taɓ gay, taar bayne ko.
Gintu menaw seer, Peliks astu Meser iŋ daaciy Durusila taat min *Yuudinnaɗo. Ŋu dakiig gas Pool, kar ŋa cokiyiig ŋa kaawa ɗo bi ka imaan taat ɗo Iisa Masi.
Iisa telkiiji aman: " Ki aamintu-aŋ asaan nu ɗiyiijiŋ a nu talin̰ciŋ ɗo baat ta *pigiye-aŋka. Ka seener, kii tale gamin kuuk ajbay pak ŋuur-aŋku! "
Iŋ aando ƴiriyo ho aando, ŋa goy ɗo maggindi iŋ ka dambar ho ŋa koolaw. Ŋa alaw ho ŋa muuti iŋ dambay.
Taar kaak weeyig zi ka gemor, taar zi ka gemor. Kar taar taat weeyig Ruwwin ta Buŋdi gay, taar ruwwine.
Iisa kaawiico pa-ak, kar ŋa ɗiyiico pey aman: " Lazaar, royinte, ŋaar weƴaw, kar nu ɓaa nooyin̰ji. "
Way gaaƴiƴco ɗo gee-aŋku asaan ŋuur ic botol ta Kayen! Ŋu ic botol ta Balaam, ŋu bariya botol ta maaniico a ŋuu gase malle. Ɗo botol-at ko, ŋu gaɗtu ko ziŋkico asaan ŋu poocig Kayen. Ho ar kaak awalle, gee ŋuur-ak, Buŋ deeyiigu asaan ŋu poociit kaawoy ta Koraas ho ŋa deeyiigu oki.
Buŋ nooyig Rabbin Iisa Masi min ɗo muuti ho ginte oki, ŋaate nooyinte iŋ gudurrey.
Min Simon Piyer taliig pa-ak, ŋa dersitu ɗo asin̰ji ku Iisa ho ŋa ɗiytu aman: " Gem kol *Rabbiney, ɗeet annere, nu gem kaak gin zunuubinna. "
Min Pilaat ibintu kadar ŋa gediraaɗo gine maan ka maala, illa ŋa raka a wer yaa barjile di. Hiyya, ŋa sokiig amay ho ŋa aciig pisin̰ji ɗo uŋco ka geemir. Kar ŋa ɗiytu aman: " Baana! Ya ɗo gaaƴar ka gem-aŋ, nun nigeɗo kaƴar min ɗo kaar. Taloŋ, aŋ kuŋkoŋ ko kuŋko. "
Galal ɗo taar taat aamin kadar kaaw taat Rabbin Buŋ kaawiititi-at yaa ase ɗo werti! "
Ŋaar kaak diyaat pikirrey ɗo galal ta ziŋkar di, ŋaar iyaat muutu. Kar gay, ya ŋa diyaat pikirre ɗo Ruwwin ta Buŋdi, ŋaar iyaat goye ka gaasɗo ho ŋa iyaat aapiye.
Ŋaar goy ɗo duniiner. Ŋaar ar Buŋ, kar gay, iŋ ŋaar di, Buŋ ginno botol taat ŋaa nece ar ŋaar di.
Asaan wiktin taat nu goyiy ɗo geeger ka Tesalonik sa, ku berdu gaayko dees dakina ɗo wiktin taat ya gamin arumdu.
Min ŋa un̰jitu ɗo ger ka salaaner-ak, gin gem rakki aariɗ obga. Ŋa aariɗ obga. Ɗo wer-ak, ŋa kooltu raɗa aman:
Ŋu kaawiy ɗo dambiniidi ho ɗo kotat aman: " Sollonni ɗo kaƴni ho cigilinni min uŋji ka ŋaar kaak goy ka sees ka Sultan ho min dapin̰ko ta *Roŋ Tamgi.
Daatko-at kaawiiji aman: " Gem kol Rabbiney, kaawon̰-an ka seener. Illa kan̰ sa, ŋuur tiya meerin kuuk gaama min ɗo pise ka kooginar di. "
Ɗo wiktin taat gee cokiyiy kaawin-ak, Iisa deltu pey daŋla rakki, asaan ŋa gaay ko moota iŋ Zeruzaleem ho gee-ak gay pakira a *Meennaw ta Buŋdi yaa bayne koɗok-koɗok.
Ka seener, ŋa Buŋ ko kaak siyte gii nece ɗo gamin-aŋku. Ŋa berte Ruwwiney ar maan kaak as awalle min awalle. Maan kaak gii gasin̰-ak, ŋaar ko gaare kadar gamin kuuk yaa ase neginda, gii gasin̰ iŋ uŋji.
Kar nu taltu pey *ɗubil ka Buŋdi ka pey ɗukuma ɗatik ucer. Ŋa gin Kabarre ta Gala taat yaa goye doo ɗo gee kuuk goy ɗo adiy ka kiɗar, ɗo ay tamba, ay tamba, ay caaro, ay kaawo ho ay darre.
Taar gay amiltu kara ho ta indiit yaaco aman: " Naa inde maa kaak naaji inde? " Taar gay telkiiji aman: " Naa inde kaay ka Yaaya-Batist. "
*Aristaark kaak goy iŋ nunu ɗo daŋaayner sa, ooyko. Maark kaak nu kaawkoŋ ko biy iŋ Barnabaas oki ooyko dakina. Ya ŋa as ɗo werko, obig samaane.
Ɗo wiktin taar-at, iidin ta *Yuudinnar taat ŋu koliy Paak gaaye, Iisa ɓaawtu Zeruzaleem.
Riy taat Buŋ giniy ɗo geemir, taar biyuwti dakina. Kar Buŋ gay, ŋaar rakki di kaak ginaag gamin okin̰co-aŋ ɗo gee okin̰co.
Min pa-ak, Iisa koliig okin̰co ho ŋa kaawiico iŋ dele ka daŋlal aman: " Maman *Seetanne yaa gedire atke Seetanne?
Ɗo bi ŋaar-aŋ ko, gee ku Buŋdi yaa ice subirraw, ŋuur kuuk karmiyaag *gaanuun ka Buŋdi ho kuuk aamin ɗo Iisa Masi.
Kar gay, ɗo ŋuur kuuk Buŋ koltu, kuuk Yuudinna iŋ kuuk Yuudinnaɗo oki, Iisa Masi, ŋaar gudurre ta Buŋdi ho ilim ta Buŋdi.
*Agindaw ku Yuudinnar kuuk goy ɗo iidin-at bariyiy Iisa ho ŋu indiy aman: " Ŋaar gay goy momo? "
Ɗo wer-ak, okintini ni galtu bup. Min ni galtu, nu dortu gaaƴ ar ta gemor kolaan iŋ kaaw ta *Yuudinnar aman: ‟ Sawuul, Sawuul, maa di ki taaɓiyiin ampa-aŋka? Maan biida-aŋ patiy kaar tak-tak! "
Kuun bariyindu ho ku gasaanno, asaan ku gediraaɗo ɓaawe wer kaak nu ɓaayiyo. "
Gem kol siŋtay, indiguwoŋ Buŋ ɗo bi kani.
Ɗo wiktin taar-at, gee dakin aale n̰umtu nam ŋu tirƴa ziŋkico nam ŋu tirƴa ziŋkico. Ɗo wer-ak, Iisa teestu kaawe awalle ɗo maajirnay aman: " Goyoŋ goɗom min gel ta Pariziyennar. Gelbinko-aŋ gaara kadar ŋu gee kuuk kaawa iŋ biŋkico di.
Ka seener, ŋu siir ɗo *gaanuun ka Rabbin Buŋ aman: " Ay gem kaak aawo awalle-ak, illa ŋaa rase ziy ɗo Rabbiner. "
Yampa, ɗo botol ta Rabbinte, daatik goyɗo ɗatik ta mitkor ho mitik sa goyɗo ɗatik ta daatkor.
Ya ɗo tan̰ji-at, ŋa pakira a Buŋ gin gudurre taat ŋaa nooyin̰ gee min ɗo muuti. Ampaa ko, ta ar awalle oki, min Isaaka nooytu min ɗo muuti, Ibraayim ooytu oki.
Gem kol siŋtay, iŋ selliŋkuwiy taat Buŋ gintu-an, nu taaƴaako a kuu berguwe ziŋkiko ɗo Buŋdi ar *satkin taat goy mento, taat *cawar ho taat aawaaji gala. Ampa-ak, ŋaar-ak ko riy taat ku giniy iŋ gelbinko.
Ŋu jag min seen ta Buŋdi. Ŋu kaawa a Buŋ nooyig gee kuuk mate, ho diŋ gay, ŋu nigaag imaan ta gee daarin̰.
Ampa-ak, tamba ta Ibraayim yoo ta Dawuud, okintiti orok iŋ pooɗ. Min Dawuud ŋu iyiig gee ku Babiloon-ak, orok iŋ pooɗ. Kar min ŋu iyiig gee ku Babiloon-ak yoo Iisa Masi gay, orok iŋ pooɗ.
Nu gin gudurre ɗo gamin okin̰co iŋ gudurre ta Iisa Masi taat beraadu gudurre.
Zer, ya nu bal ase ho nu bal kaawe ɗo geemir, ŋu ginno zunuubinna. Kar diŋ gay, ŋu ginno botol taat ŋuu imile ziŋkico ɗo bi ka zunuubinnico.
Diŋ gay, n̰aam gee Jappa, ŋu ɓaayiy kole gem rakki siŋji Simon kaak ŋu koliy oki Piyer.
Nu berko gudurre taat kuu jaawe kaaco ka aalin kuuk ar aalin kuuk aalin-aŋku ho kuuk ar aalin-aŋku. Gudurre-at, ku gediraaɗo pey gine maan kaak samaanno.
Hiyya, Pool iŋ Barnabaas gay telkiico bal kolaw aman: " Illa nin kat zer yaako gaarin kaaw ta Buŋdi awalle. Kar gay, kuŋ gay poocit Kabarre ta Gala-an, ku ibanno kadar ku turro gase goye ka gaasɗo. Diŋ gay, ni ic botol ta gee kuuk Yuudinnaɗo.
Pariziyenna-ak indiig pey aman: " Ya kiŋ bal gine Masi, wal *Eli, wal nabiin̰ce kaak ŋu kaawtu awalle-ak, maa di ki batiziyiy gee? "
Min Iisa kaawtu pa-ak, ŋa kooltu raɗa aman: " Lazaar, amil kara! "
Adin ku gemor, illa gee kuuk goy ɗo geriy ka meen̰ji di. "
Ɗo wer-ak, gem kaak siŋji Sawuul-ak, ŋa bariya botol taat taaɓiyin̰ gee ku Eglizdi. Ŋa un̰ja ɗo geriyco, ŋa obig gee kuuk miday iŋ kuuk daaɗi, ŋa obig daŋaayne.
asaan ŋa elgig darrite ho ŋa ŋaar ko kaak pinig ger ka salaaner. "
Ŋaar-aŋ ko gaarkoŋ ko Kabarre ta Gala-ata. Kabarre-at gaaya gaayen di ho ta totira ɗo duniin okintiti. Uudin taat ta kuuniy min ƴiriy taat ku doriit kabarre-ata ho ku ibiniit barkin ta Buŋdi iŋ seen ta meen̰ji.
Kar gay, nu kaawaako, Eli ŋaar as ko, kar gee gay ginig gamin okin̰co kuuk ŋu raktu uudin taat ŋu siirtu ɗo Kitamner ɗo bi kan̰ji. "
Min pa-ak, Iisa teestu kaawe daŋla ɗo geemir aman: " Cokiyoŋ! Gin gem rakki taat taat taat taat taat taat taat taate jineendi. Ŋa taattu atay ho ŋa ɗuuniig iŋ durdurre. Ŋa ɗuuniig wer a ŋuu miƴin̰ji ɗo jineendi-aka. Kar ŋa siyiig wer rakki a ŋuu gooƴin̰ji ɗo jineendi-aka. Kar ŋa siytu wer ka gooƴindi a ŋuu gooƴin̰ji. Hiyya, ŋa rasig jineen-ak ɗo gee daarin̰ a ŋuu gooƴin̰ji ho ŋa ɗeettu marti.
Kar ŋa kaawiico ɗo ŋuur kuuk suugiya ammaamna-ak aman: " Imiloŋ gamin-aŋ min anne! Ger ka Tanni, dakoŋ ginin̰jiɗo ar ger ka suuginer! "
Iisa gay ɗiyiico aman: " Kaawon̰co ɗo gee-aŋ a ŋuu goye keɗer. " Ɗo wer-ak, gin gan̰ dakina kuuk balan̰. Ɗo wer-ak, miday goytu, ŋuu nece ar gee alip beeƴ pa.
Ŋaar gay telkiico aman: " Dakoŋ kappiyenno maan pak taat ŋu diyiiko. "
Pariziyenna-ak telkiiji aman: " Muusa gay ber botol taat gem yaa siire maktumne ta totiriikar ho ŋaa totirin̰ daatko. "
Asaan iŋ ilim ta Buŋdi oki, gee ku duniiner bal ibinin̰ Buŋ iŋ ilimco-ata. Kar gay, iŋ maan kaak arro ka Kabarre ta Gala-at, Buŋ ictu niyine a ŋaa jilin̰ ŋuur kuuk aamin iŋ ŋaara.
Min ŋaar-ak, Seetanne iyiig Iisa pey ka damba taat bolok aale ho ŋa gaariijig kiɗin ku sultinniidi okin̰co ku duniiner iŋ mallico.
Min nu jaaliig pey kaar, nu dortu gaɗi ar sersir kaak coona kuwa ka samaaner. Ŋa kooltu iŋ gaaƴ toŋgo aman: " Ɗo gaaƴiƴko, ɗo gaaƴiƴko kuŋ gee kuuk goy ɗo adiy ka kiɗar, ɗo gaaƴiƴko asaan perne taat ɗubal ku Buŋdi kuuk subba-aŋ raka paane! "
Gee ku Egliz ka Antiyoos-ak, gin nabiinna daarin̰ ho daarin̰ kuuk ɓilda gee iŋ kaawin kuuk ɓilda gee iŋ kaaw ta Buŋdi. Minninco goy Barnabaas, Simon kaak ŋu koliy oki " Gay marbinto," Lisiyuus min geeger ka Sireen, Lazaar kaak gin pisin̰ji iŋ pisin̰ji ka sultan *Herood ho iŋ Sawuul oki.
Min ŋaar-ak, *Pariziyenna sin̰jiiji moota ɗo Iisa ho ŋu teestu indin̰ji iŋ kaawin dakina, ŋu rakiiji ɗibe. Ŋu indiig a ŋaaco gaare maan kaak ajbay kaak asa min ɗo Buŋdi.
Pool iŋ een̰ji, ŋu uctu min geeger ka Papoos ho ŋu n̰eptu markaba, ŋu birtu ɗo geeger ka Perz ɗo kiɗ ka Pampili. Kar wiktin taar-at, Yaaya-Batist rasiigu ho ŋu yeeptu Zeruzaleem.
Ɗo adiy ka kiɗar, sultinnay okin̰co ɓaaƴit ko ɓaaƴe mun̰jam ho gee ku adiy ka kiɗar sa sakriyaw iŋ ɓaaƴinti. "
Ɗo wer kaak ŋu ɗooɗiig Iisa-ak, gin jineene rakki. Ɗo jineen-ak gay, gin magin taat marbinto. Ɗo magin-at, yoo momte rakki oki ŋu balti diye tak-tak.
Kar ya nu atka aariɗna iŋ gudurre ta Buŋdi, ŋaar-ak gaara kadar *Meennaw ta Buŋdi askoŋ ko loko.
Rabbin Iisa kolsiig Piyer ho ŋa taliig odinay. Ek di Piyer moyiit kaaw taat Rabbin kaawiiji aman: " Ƴiriyta-aŋ, kokir boogaaɗo diŋka, kii tatire dees subba a ki ibinginno. "
Kar ɗo uŋji ka sees ka sultan gay, gin maan ar barre kaak irn̰a ɓarlin̰-ɓarlin̰ ar serpe ta hadinner. Ɗo ɗatik ta sees ka sultan gay, gin gamin kuuk siikimaw pooɗ di kuuk odinco odinco odinco rakki ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Min agindaw ku Yuudinnar doriit kaaw-at, ŋu ɗiytu aman: " Ŋa raka deen̰ ziy walla? Ya ŋa kaawa pa-ak, ŋa ɗiya aman: ‟ Kuŋ gediraaɗo ɓaawe wer kaak nu ɓaayiyo. " "
Ni talgigɗo pey waan kaak as iŋ odinay ɗo geriy a ŋaa ozilin̰ Buŋ. Illa gem-aŋ di as iŋ ŋaar kaak as min darre-anta walla? "
Oboŋ goroŋ gamin kuuk eeŋko yaa ozilin̰co, ho ar taar-an ko, kuu necin taat gaanuun ka Iisa Masi kaawtu.
ho ŋa kaawiiji aman: ‟ Amal, rasig darren̰ ho iŋ gee ku meen̰jiŋ, ɓaa ɗo darre taat naaji gaare. "
Ooyon̰co ɗo siŋta kuuk goy ɗo geeger ka Lawodiise ho ɗo siŋti Nampi iŋ gee ku Eglizdi kuuk n̰uma gerti.
Paa kat, kuu gedire ibinin̰ gamin kuuk taɓ paka. Paa kat, kuu goye *cawar ho bal oorne ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi nam ƴiriy taat Iisa Masi yaa yeepe ɗo duniiner.
" Goyoŋ goɗom min agindaw ku gaanuundi kuuk el ise kesuun taat samaane ɗo uŋco ka geemir. Ŋu el a gee yaaco jaawe iŋ karaamine ɗo werin kuuk gee n̰umiyo. Ɗo geray ku salaaner, ŋu el goye uŋda ho ya ŋu kolig ɗo teendi, ŋu doɓa werin kuuk taɓ.
Kar ya kuŋ gee ku Iisa Masi-ak, ku gin ko ko koogin ku Ibraayim ho Buŋ kaawtu a ŋaaji bere gamin kuuk ŋa kaawtu a ŋaaji bere.
Hiyya, askirna-ak ɗukumiig mernan kuuk ɗuunig markab kaak kapak-aka, ŋu rasiiga ho ŋu rasiig ŋa ɗeettu iŋ amay.
Min ŋaar-ak, maajirnay kuuk orok iŋ rakki ɗeettu ɗo kiɗ ka Galile, ŋu ɓaawtu ka dambar taat Iisa kaawiico.
Iŋ imaan, gee ku Israyeel jaawiig durdurre ka geeger ka Zeriiko. Wiktin taat ŋu jaawtu ɗo geeger-ak, ŋu jaawtu, kar durdurre-at eeztu.
Ɗo ger ka salaaner ka Yuudinnar-ak, gin gem rakki aariɗ obga. Min ŋa un̰jitu, ŋa teestu koole raɗa aman:
Ŋaar kat mat ɗo bi ka gee okin̰co. Ŋa mattu-ak a ŋuur kuuk goy misa iŋ odinco, ŋu goyaaɗo pey tak-tak ɗo bi ka goyin̰co kaak yaa ase neginda. Kar gay, ŋa mat ɗo bi ka ŋaar kaak mat ɗo bi kan̰co ho kaak nooytu ɗo saan tan̰co-aka.
Min ŋa nooye, ŋa bayniiji ɗo Zaak, kar kat ŋa bayniig ɗo paliinna okin̰co.
Ansi-ak, onyoŋ kaƴko ɗo pise ka Buŋdi ho ɗo pise ka pisin̰ji kaak gin gudurre dakina. Paa kat, ɗo wiktin taat ŋa rakiy di, ŋaako jaaliŋko kuwa.
Goytu kee, nu bal talin pey uŋda asaan portikaw-at patiy kaar. Ampaa ko, ŋuur kuuk goy iŋ nunu, beriidu pise nam nu ottu ɗo geeger ka Damaas.
Ɗo wiktin taar-at, maajirnay marmiliiji ɗo Iisa aman: " Gem kol Tacco, berni tee! "
Ya nu ɓaa ɗo werko, ku raka naako iyin̰ maa? Ku raka naako iye taaɓine walla? Wal naako gine dalullay ho dalullay?
Ba aaro, ƴiriy rakki, Herood iidiytu iidin ta weendi. Hiyya, ƴiriy taar-at, Herood iidiytu iidin taat agindaw ku askirnay iŋ aginduwco okin̰co ho iŋ gee ku darrer ku Galile.
Iŋ ƴiriy ta dumaas, wer dugus-dugus sabaan cokaw, Mariyam taat min Magdala ɓaawtu ɗo maginer. Ta taliig dambi kaak ŋu goottu ɗo bit ka maginer-ak waan tuŋkilga.
Dakni rasenno *Seetanne yaa gecinti, kar gay, jilinni min ɗo *Seetanner. " "
Diŋka-aŋ, iŋ taaɓin taat goy diŋka-anta, nu pakira a samaane kuu goye goye ar taat ku goyiy-aŋka.
Ŋa berco gamin kuuk mey diyaaco, ŋa berco gamin kuuk samaane, ho gay gamnar gay, ŋa n̰aamiig pisin̰co orok.
Ɗo wer-ak, ŋa dortu gaaƴ kaawa min kuwa ka samaaner aman: " Ŋaar-aŋ roŋdu, nu elgig dakina ho adir miin iŋ galal ɗo bi kan̰ji. "
" Nun gay kaawaako aman: Ginoŋ iŋ malle ka duniiner. Ampa-ak, bariyoŋ botol taat kuu gine roynay ku taɓ. Paa kat, ya malle-ak gaase, gee-ak yaako ŋaamiŋko ɗo goye kaak taɓ. "
Ka seener gay, nun *Roŋ gemor di mee sabitdi. "
Ya ku talaagu, ya ŋu leeyaw, ku iban ko iŋ odinko kadar kabuŋ gaaye.
Gee kuuk Buŋ kilgiytu iŋ kiɗa, ŋuur oki ar ŋaar kaak Buŋ kilgiytu iŋ kiɗa. Gee kuuk as ase min kuwa, ŋuur oki ar ŋaar kaak as ase min kuwa.
" Ku dor ŋu kaaw pey aman: ‟ Od iŋ od, saaŋ iŋ saaŋ ho saaŋ iŋ saaŋ iŋ saaŋ. "
Daatik rakki min gee ku Kanaani taat asa min ɗo kiɗar-ak asiiji moota ho ta teestu koole aman: " Gem kol *Rabbinni, *Roŋ ka Dawuud, tal aminduwir. Romor, taar aariɗ obta. Ta taaɓiya dakina. "
Ka seener gay, Buŋ diyig *mee satkiner ka tatko kaak taɓ, ar kaak awalle, ŋa diyig Melkisedek-aka.
Ɗo wer-ak, ŋu ɗooɗiig oki kokinay seera ɗo et ka Iisa. Ka rakki ɗo meeday ho ka rakki gay ɗo n̰ugilay.
Min ŋaar-ak, maajirnay paaytu ka markabar di, ŋu ɗeettu keeco ɗo wer ka maala.
Wiktin taat Iisa ɓaay Zeruzaleem, ŋa koliig maajirnay kuuk orok iŋ seera ho ŋa kaawiico aman:
Ya gemko-ak imaanjiy sooɗ-ak, obig samaane. Kar gay, dakon̰ji ɗukume seriinenno ɗo bi ka kaawin daarin̰ kuuk aditco osaw di.
Ka seener, ya gem kat siirig malley okin̰ji ɗo kooginay ɗo kooginay, ŋaar-ak gin botol taat ŋaa goye iŋ ŋaara ya gem-ak mat di. Yampa, ŋa goyɗo iŋ botol wiktin taat gem kaak siirig malley-ak goy mento.
Maan biida-ak iŋ geepay ku maan biida kuuk orok kuuk ki taltu-ak ƴiriy rakki, ŋu ƴilaat baar ku azbin̰ca-ata. Ŋuu taaɓiyinti tak-tak ho ŋuu rasinti tukinka. Ŋu asa teen̰ kumti ho ŋuu erin̰ iŋ ako.
Aariɗna amiltu min ɗo gee dakina iŋ koriyco ho iŋ koriyay oki, gee dakina kuuk ziŋkico galcoɗo iŋ kuuk ziŋkico galcoɗo cooltu.
Nu siiraat lociŋ ɗo kiŋ Timote, kiŋ ar roŋdu kaak nu elgiy dakina. Tatte Buŋ ho iŋ Rabbinte Iisa Masi, ŋuun̰ barkiye, ŋuu tale aminduwin̰ ho ŋuun̰ iye aapiye.
Kar Iisa kaawiico ɗo gee okin̰co aman: " Ya gem kaak rakaan aaɗindu, ŋaa pooce pey bariye galal ta meen̰ji, ŋaa icin̰ etoy ka taaɓiner kun kawta ho ŋaan aaɗindu.
Ay gem di, illa ŋaa goye ɗo goyin̰ji kaak ɗo wiktin taat Buŋ koliiga.
Min maajirnay taliig maanna-ak, ŋu dapin̰tu aale ho ŋu ɗiytu aman: " Way, kaawoy-an samaanno!
Dees beeƴ, Yuudinna koocintu orok pooɗ iŋ orok pooɗ iŋ rakki di.
Hiyya, min wiktin taat kun̰ Mariyam iŋ Yuusup nectu ɗo gaanuun ka Muusa a ŋuu gine *cawar ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, ŋu iciig Iisa Zeruzaleem a ŋuu gaarin̰ji ɗo Rabbin Buŋ
Kar gin oki nabiin̰ca rakki siŋti Anna. Ta romti ka Panuweel, min caar ka Azeer. Ta zaɓ ko ho ta goy ko iŋ mitti ko elgin peesira. Min ŋu obit mitti-ak di, ta goy pey iŋ mitti, kar kat ta goy ko elgin peesira.
Buŋ oki goy saadinnay kuuk gaara kadar gamin kuuk ajbay iŋ kuuk gaara gudurrey dakina. Ŋa ɗeeɗiig gamin kuuk ajbay aale-aku. Ŋa ɗeeɗiig gamin kuuk Ruwwiney taat ŋa beriico ɗo geemir uudin ta niyin ta meen̰ji.
